# 🎓 BrightPath Learning Center

BrightPath Learning Center is a responsive educational website developed as part of the **MANTRA 2026 Summer School – Frontend Website Assignment**. The project demonstrates the fundamentals of frontend web development, responsive design, SEO, and website deployment.

## 🌐 Live Demo

**Website:** https://mantra-asssignment-one.netlify.app/home

## 📖 Project Overview

BrightPath Learning Center is a fictional educational institute website designed to provide visitors with information about courses, faculty, learning resources, and admissions. The website follows a clean and modern design while maintaining simplicity and usability.

## ✨ Features

* Responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
* Multi-page website with consistent navigation
* Modern educational theme
* Course listings with pricing and details
* Image gallery
* Contact and registration form
* JavaScript form validation
* Semantic HTML5 structure
* Basic SEO implementation
* Flexbox-based layouts
* Clean and user-friendly interface

## 📄 Website Pages

* Home
* About
* Courses
* Gallery
* Contact

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript
* Flexbox
* GitHub
* Netlify

## 📱 Responsive Design

The website has been designed to work seamlessly across different screen sizes, including:

* Desktop
* Laptop
* Tablet
* Mobile Devices

## 🔍 SEO Features

* Optimized page titles
* Meta descriptions
* Semantic heading structure
* Meaningful image alt attributes
* Simple and descriptive page names

